export interface Avatar {
  id: string;
  svg: string;
  description: string;
}

export const avatars: Avatar[] = [
  {
    id: '1',
    description: 'Молодой мужчина',
    svg: `<svg viewBox="0 0 100 100" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
      <defs>
        <linearGradient id="avatarGradient" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%">
          <stop offset="0%" style="stop-color:#c084fc;stop-opacity:0.2"/>
          <stop offset="100%" style="stop-color:#a855f7;stop-opacity:0.4"/>
        </linearGradient>
        <filter id="glow">
          <feGaussianBlur stdDeviation="2" result="coloredBlur"/>
          <feMerge>
            <feMergeNode in="coloredBlur"/>
            <feMergeNode in="SourceGraphic"/>
          </feMerge>
        </filter>
      </defs>
      <circle cx="50" cy="50" r="45" fill="url(#avatarGradient)" stroke="#d8b4fe" stroke-width="1"/>
      <circle cx="50" cy="40" r="20" fill="#581c87" filter="url(#glow)"/>
      <path d="M30 80 Q50 60 70 80" stroke="#7e22ce" stroke-width="2" fill="none" filter="url(#glow)"/>
      <path d="M25 75 L75 75" stroke="#d8b4fe" stroke-width="0.5" stroke-dasharray="2 2"/>
      <path d="M35 85 L65 85" stroke="#d8b4fe" stroke-width="0.5" stroke-dasharray="2 2"/>
      <circle cx="35" cy="35" r="2" fill="#d8b4fe"/>
      <circle cx="65" cy="35" r="2" fill="#d8b4fe"/>
    </svg>`
  },
  {
    id: '2',
    description: 'Молодая женщина',
    svg: `<svg viewBox="0 0 100 100" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
      <circle cx="50" cy="50" r="45" fill="#f3f4f6"/>
      <circle cx="50" cy="40" r="20" fill="#4b5563"/>
      <path d="M30 80 Q50 60 70 80" stroke="#4b5563" stroke-width="4" fill="none"/>
      <path d="M40 30 Q50 20 60 30" stroke="#4b5563" stroke-width="2" fill="none"/>
    </svg>`
  }
];
